--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party data sources
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

MiSonos retrieves content from third-party services at the user's direction.
Users are responsible for complying with each service's terms of use:

  - YouTube Music: accessed via the user's own pasted browser cookies; this may
    be subject to YouTube's Terms of Service.
  - Internet Archive Live Music Archive (etree) and Grateful Dead collection.
  - phish.in API.
  - Podcast Index (https://podcastindex.org) and the Apple Podcasts directory
    for podcast discovery; episodes are played from each podcast's own RSS feed.
  - Apple iTunes Search API for cover-art lookups.
  - TuneIn / RadioTime OPML directory (https://opml.radiotime.com) for internet
    radio discovery; stations stream from each broadcaster's own server.

